name: Insect Jungle
overview: Insect Jungle is a French language Centipede clone for the Commodore 64. It was developed by a Josselin Chenet and published in the following: Hebdogiciel N°142 (04.07.1986) + N°143 (11.07.1986) + N°144 (18.07.1986). Fight fiercely against the vermin crawling in your Commodore as a result of an obvious lack of maintenance, you'll need to make the best use of your joystick (in port 2) for controlled cleaning.
